                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "value": "The rain hadn't stopped for three days. It drummed against the window of my office, a relentless rhythm that matched the pounding in my head."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "image",
                        "value": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1478720568477-152d9b164e63?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "value": "I picked up the phone. The voice on the other end was distorted, but the message was clear: 'They found it.'"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": "Part 2: The Underground",
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "value": "I descended into the subway tunnels, the air growing colder with every step."
                    }
                ]
            }
